WEBVTT

00:49.299 --> 00:51.968
STILL SHINING

01:00.685 --> 01:05.940
MARCH 2021

01:06.900 --> 01:08.151
Hello, sir.

01:09.736 --> 01:11.571
Wag kang masyadong magalang dito.

01:13.198 --> 01:14.199
Okay po.

01:15.283 --> 01:17.744
Magandang mag-programming
pag madaling-araw.

01:18.745 --> 01:19.746
Tahimik.

01:33.635 --> 01:35.345
Sina Lola't Lolo naman,

01:36.638 --> 01:38.097
masayang may trabaho ako

01:38.723 --> 01:41.351
kaya laging nanlilibre sa mga kapitbahay.

01:43.394 --> 01:44.521
At si Hui-seo…

01:47.148 --> 01:48.233
Mas masaya.

01:49.150 --> 01:50.568
Lagi niyang sinasabi.

01:51.820 --> 01:53.279
Ngayon lang ako nakakita

01:53.947 --> 01:55.907
ng hayagang magsabing masaya siya.

01:57.867 --> 01:59.452
Akala ko, di totoo.

02:04.207 --> 02:05.333
Kakaiba.

02:08.002 --> 02:09.045
Ako naman…

02:12.382 --> 02:13.633
Kasi…

02:16.136 --> 02:17.971
Mahalaga pa ba 'yon?

02:24.144 --> 02:31.109
STILL SHINING

02:34.112 --> 02:36.614
<i>Paparating na ang tren.</i>

02:37.490 --> 02:41.953
